AVERMEDIA TECH said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 51.68% to NT$107,136,000 from NT$221,708,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            107,136          221,708    
YOY%             -51.68%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            495,072         1,039,516   
YOY%             -52.37% 
=================================================================
 